WEBVTT

00:02.639 --> 00:06.714
This is a recording of the advice
given by her Holiness Mataji Nirmala Devi,

00:06.914 --> 00:10.733
on 22nd March 1977,

00:10.933 --> 00:12.850
at Bhakti Vidya Bhavana,

00:13.050 --> 00:17.537
in the form of questions and answers.

00:23.006 --> 01:27.120
[Shri Mataji speaks Hindi and Marathi]

01:27.321 --> 01:29.800
They have mastered the Kundalini completely.

01:30.000 --> 01:31.999
There are some, you know that,

01:32.199 --> 01:37.132
but there are some who have got
realization last five years and they don’t know a word.

01:37.333 --> 01:41.209
On the contrary, they’ll just come and
ask us, “My mother is ill. So please treat her.”

01:41.409 --> 01:44.067
“My father is ill.” “You treat me.” “My this thing is ill.”

01:44.267 --> 01:46.535
That’s all. They are good for nothing.

01:46.736 --> 01:50.694
So now you have to also give to others and you have too,

01:50.895 --> 01:55.652
realize yourself and to be the light of Sahaja Yoga.

01:55.852 --> 01:59.998
It’s a great pleasure. It’s a
greatest joy, to give it to others,

02:00.198 --> 02:05.784
and you don’t have to spend any money for
that and you don’t have to earn any money for that.

02:05.984 --> 02:09.455
It is just a free flow. But you must give.

02:09.736 --> 02:13.249
Otherwise, if you do not give then you stagnate;

02:14.147 --> 02:15.961
absolutely, it stagnates.

02:16.161 --> 02:19.136
Today we have so many people
over here, I’m very happy to see.

02:19.336 --> 02:23.156
I hope you’ll keep up the
number. At least on a Monday keep it.

02:23.357 --> 02:56.013
[Shri Mataji speaks Marathi and Hindi].

02:56.214 --> 03:01.567
Sahaja Yoga is not a thing to be taken that frivolously.

03:01.767 --> 03:05.629
It works. It works in you in no time effortlessly,

03:05.860 --> 03:10.612
but after realization, for all
human beings it is necessary,

03:10.812 --> 03:15.938
to understand the complete working
of the Kundalini and of the vibrations.

03:16.138 --> 03:18.247
You must know the complete science.

03:18.447 --> 03:24.037
Otherwise, what is the use of getting money
which you do not know how to spend or use?

03:24.238 --> 03:26.382
So best thing is to get to it

03:26.583 --> 03:32.220
and by you will find that even if
you are sick and cured by Sahaja Yoga,

03:32.420 --> 03:35.668
you’ll find you’ll become so much healthier and better.

03:35.868 --> 03:37.769
You’ll be enriched much more.

03:37.970 --> 03:43.819
If you do not take to Sahaja Yoga, gradually
you’ll find your vibrations will be lost after some time,

03:44.019 --> 03:49.233
because God doesn’t want to waste His vibrations on people,

03:49.433 --> 03:51.996
who do not want to give it to others.

03:53.092 --> 03:55.690
There are some people who give explanations,

03:55.890 --> 04:01.766
“We have a family. How are we to give up?” Now I
have also family. You know I have grandchildren also.

04:03.029 --> 04:07.302
This is the only good thing
you can do without paying a single pie.

04:07.502 --> 04:09.988
You have got it without paying a single pie and

04:10.088 --> 04:12.567
you have to distribute also without paying a,

04:12.767 --> 04:15.836
single pie and you have to enjoy yourself.

04:16.037 --> 04:19.733
Only you can enjoy if you can give.

04:20.688 --> 04:25.717
You have to learn all these things.
By God’s grace you have so many people here.

04:25.918 --> 04:28.643
Here now at least fifty percent people, I would say,

04:28.843 --> 04:33.227
are such that they can tell you about Kundalini quite well

04:33.691 --> 04:36.114
and you they are going to work out with you.

04:36.214 --> 04:38.597
They are going to tell you about this; nothing to feel bad,

04:38.797 --> 04:42.204
because once you master the
Kundalini you will become just the same.

04:42.405 --> 04:45.837
So there is nothing to feel
superior or inferior or anything.

04:46.037 --> 04:49.900
Only thing is that you today you
have jumped into the sea and you have,

04:50.100 --> 04:53.825
learnt how to swim and they have learnt it long time back,

04:54.025 --> 04:58.056
and gradually you’ll pick up very
fast. Some people pick up so fast,

04:58.256 --> 05:04.723
that it’s sometimes astonishingly speedy,

05:04.923 --> 05:08.109
and even the people who,

05:08.309 --> 05:12.423
have been with Me for years cannot beat them.

05:12.624 --> 05:18.655
So, it is only your simplicity and
earnestness to be that. You work it out very well.

05:20.131 --> 05:25.985
Aata, I would like you to ask Me
questions because when I go away I don’t want,

05:26.185 --> 05:29.101
the half-hearted people to ask questions

05:29.302 --> 05:31.920
because then the, if the questions start, then the

05:32.020 --> 05:34.631
murmuring souls will start and they will try to,

05:34.831 --> 05:40.720
bring out people who are not yet
half-baked, and then they will fizzle out.

05:40.921 --> 05:44.207
So, you have to completely mature into Sahaja Yoga.

05:44.407 --> 05:47.482
Do not listen to anybody because he says so.

05:47.683 --> 05:51.053
You ask him, “What is your authority?
Do you know anything about Kundalini?

05:51.254 --> 05:53.829
Have you, how many people you have given realization to?

05:54.029 --> 05:58.693
How many people you have given jagruti
to? None. Then you keep quiet.” That’s all.

05:58.894 --> 06:01.176
You have seen Kundalini moving.

06:01.376 --> 06:03.567
You have seen its pulsation.

06:03.767 --> 06:08.747
You have felt the vibrations.
Now, anybody who talks about against,

06:08.947 --> 06:13.486
Sahaja Yoga is very easy, anybody
can, any Dick, Tom and Harry can say,

06:13.788 --> 06:16.466
very easy to criticize anything,

06:16.666 --> 06:20.521
very easy because how much does it
take? You don’t need any capital for that.

06:20.722 --> 06:23.128
You need not be knowing a word about Kundalini.

06:23.328 --> 06:25.738
Some might say it’s a myth, it’s a psychological

06:25.838 --> 06:28.143
thing; all kinds of nonsense they will say.

06:28.343 --> 06:30.605
But if you are a serious people, then you must

06:30.705 --> 06:33.067
understand that you have felt the vibrations,

06:33.267 --> 06:36.922
they are there, and that you are going to proceed further.

06:37.123 --> 06:41.567
It is for your own good and for
your own asking you should get it.

06:41.767 --> 06:47.512
If there are certain problems on your chakras
they must be corrected. So, what is the question now?

06:53.980 --> 06:58.980
Yogi: What is the ego and
superego and Why God has given this to us?

07:00.251 --> 07:05.675
Shri Mataji: Ego and superego; these are the
two institutions. They grow within us as we grow,

07:05.949 --> 07:12.274
older and older because when we start growing.

07:12.640 --> 07:16.009
I’ll give you an example how the ego and super-ego grow.

07:16.209 --> 07:20.748
A mother is nursing the child, and the child is in complete...

07:24.383 --> 07:29.791
The mother is in complete
bliss when the child is being nursed.

07:31.648 --> 07:34.135
Now, what happens,

07:34.335 --> 07:39.450
when the mother moves the child to
another side, then the child doesn’t like it.

07:39.651 --> 07:43.559
So he puts in a reaction. This reaction comes in..

07:43.759 --> 07:48.135
[Don’t look there. They are not minister.

07:48.335 --> 07:53.783
He wears cap so everyone
thinks he is minister. Your attention

07:53.883 --> 07:59.255
is not here. He is just a lawyer –Marathi]

07:59.455 --> 08:02.009
...for your information haan…

08:02.209 --> 08:05.276
[Now remove that cap otherwise everyone will

08:05.376 --> 08:08.542
again think that some new minister has come,

08:08.756 --> 08:19.597
Now we should meet them last time my son did not get job.
You will think about it then. Mother is asking a person as why did

08:19.697 --> 08:30.900
you wear that cap now everyone is thinking that you are a
minister. Now people will bring application to you so don’t tell me.

08:32.250 --> 09:05.956
I will answer his question he has asked about ego & superego. Did you get my point? Now if someone go then all will see that person. How can I get benefit from that? Why human brain is so frivolous. You have something & god

09:06.056 --> 09:40.616
has given you a big head. You should give respect to it. Do not turn your eyes. Which is the thing which attract
your attention? Attention is very big thing. Attention should be pure. This is a bad habit to turn eyes – Marathi]

09:41.236 --> 09:44.469
Our eyes are ruined by because of the turning our eyes

09:44.669 --> 09:47.759
all the time here and here. Our Agnya chakra gets spoilt.

09:47.960 --> 09:50.765
You completely lose control over your eyes.

09:50.965 --> 09:54.523
Eyes are the most important things.

09:56.634 --> 10:00.900
They carry the light of your
heart of your Aatma and Spirit.

10:01.187 --> 10:04.767
At every small spot must you see?

10:05.212 --> 10:10.192
[If you want to sit then sit
& want to go then go – Marathi]

10:12.780 --> 10:17.567
This is the problem with us, that
we don’t understand our own values

10:18.600 --> 10:24.391
and we don’t understand what
should be our priority for what are we here.

10:24.592 --> 10:27.536
We must have that seriousness about ourselves.

10:28.282 --> 10:32.659
Anybody comes in or goes in or anything happening,

10:32.859 --> 10:36.087
your attention should be on to yourself.

10:36.569 --> 10:40.370
It’s very necessary at this
time when you are in meditation.

10:40.571 --> 10:44.567
This is the first time we are trying to see ourselves.

10:44.767 --> 10:47.012
So why should anybody interest us?

10:47.213 --> 10:52.181
It is only a very short time when we are –

10:53.244 --> 10:55.443
so now I’m telling you a very important thing...

10:55.644 --> 11:06.441
[At that time you come & everybody was looking at
you. It should not happen. Someone will come & someone

11:06.541 --> 11:17.334
will go but you should not look at them. Now subject
is very deep. Why god has given us ego & super-ego.

11:17.592 --> 11:19.400
It’s a very big question. - Marathi]

11:20.616 --> 11:25.924
Why God has created this ego and super-ego within us?

11:31.531 --> 11:36.558
From our stomach the medh,

11:36.758 --> 11:41.594
what you call the fat globules,
you can say medh, in the stomach,

11:41.956 --> 11:44.527
rises into our brain,

11:44.728 --> 11:47.900
passing through all these centers,

11:49.910 --> 11:53.696
evolving to be the cells of the brain.

11:53.897 --> 11:55.900
Did you follow this point?

11:56.728 --> 12:02.233
Because medh even the brain is made of fat cells,

12:03.124 --> 12:05.124
what you call the mendu.

12:05.375 --> 12:09.359
So for the medh to become the mendu,

12:09.560 --> 12:14.567
it has to evolve to achieve a certain amount,

12:14.861 --> 12:20.497
of charges of awareness of human awareness,

12:20.878 --> 12:23.233
and the brain, human brain,

12:23.433 --> 12:27.900
is the most precious one because it has a dimension,

12:28.258 --> 12:34.313
which animals do not have, a mental
dimension, you can say, an emotional dimension.

12:34.702 --> 12:39.759
Its physical dimension also has another dimension.

12:40.359 --> 12:44.827
We can say that on every dimension we have four sides.

12:45.243 --> 12:51.799
Emotionally we understand love. We
understand how to receive, how to reciprocate.

12:52.594 --> 12:56.733
We understand beauty, we understand poetry,

12:58.528 --> 13:01.900
we understand sweet gestures.

13:04.020 --> 13:08.736
We can create these things also.

13:09.369 --> 13:13.889
On the mental level our dimension has a fourth dimension,

13:14.089 --> 13:17.853
I should say, by which we create things.

13:18.054 --> 13:21.712
Animals cannot create; we can create.

13:23.030 --> 13:29.900
On the physical also we have a special advantage,

13:30.100 --> 13:34.372
that we have lifted our heads up,

13:34.648 --> 13:38.233
our hands act in a different way than our feet,

13:38.433 --> 13:41.265
we have a better capacity to hold things.

13:41.466 --> 13:46.067
Not only that but we can use this body,

13:47.941 --> 13:51.690
to lift much higher things that are here;

13:51.890 --> 13:54.652
for example, we can create a crane and lifted it.

13:54.853 --> 13:58.007
So, we have also got a power

13:58.207 --> 14:03.448
by which we can have mastery over the matter.

14:03.662 --> 14:07.294
This is not among the animals. So we have already,

14:07.495 --> 14:10.558
a higher dimension which is reached in our brain.

14:10.658 --> 14:13.567
Now, such a beautiful human brain is created.

14:15.368 --> 14:20.900
So, at this stage of human
evolution when man has reached this stage,

14:21.355 --> 14:24.080
we should say it is still in a transition.

14:24.280 --> 14:28.720
A little more he has to jump, and he
becomes that for which he has created.

14:29.353 --> 14:34.295
So, in this transition it is
necessary to protect that brain

14:34.495 --> 14:37.904
very carefully – one purpose;

14:38.105 --> 14:42.109
secondly, to make this brain independent,

14:42.310 --> 14:46.101
of the will of God and to make it use by itself,

14:46.302 --> 14:51.500
so it develops another dimension of wisdom.

14:55.268 --> 14:58.637
By faltering, by making mistakes,

14:58.837 --> 15:04.233
by correcting, by falling, by going into extremes,

15:04.433 --> 15:09.338
man starts coming in the center
and understands that this is the position.

15:09.539 --> 15:12.193
Now see in our country the political news,

15:12.393 --> 15:17.863
how from the British we came to
– British had to give us up, then we –

15:18.064 --> 15:22.131
now the new this thing we started that didn’t fail;

15:22.331 --> 15:24.703
that failed. So, we started another style.

15:24.903 --> 15:30.136
So, we started another style like that. You see, you
go on changing from this to another, experimenting,

15:30.336 --> 15:35.796
and you reach a position where you see this
is the position by which you really progress.

15:36.447 --> 15:39.169
All this is done by a human brain.

15:39.370 --> 15:42.490
So, a human brain is the most coveted thing,

15:42.690 --> 15:46.233
most evolved thing,

15:46.433 --> 15:49.733
and with the brain heart also,

15:50.205 --> 15:54.303
human heart also, has to be co-related to the brain,

15:54.503 --> 15:58.058
and so the both the things evolve very well.

15:58.259 --> 16:00.779
Our stomachs are evolved very well.

16:00.979 --> 16:03.919
Actually, our stomachs are much more,

16:04.119 --> 16:07.646
subtle and they cannot take gross things.

16:07.846 --> 16:10.611
They require very fine and

16:10.811 --> 16:14.233
sophisticated things for digestion,

16:15.013 --> 16:19.497
and so many things as you know
that we are different from animals.

16:20.676 --> 16:27.469
Now at this stage to protect this brain
also you need a kind of a hard covering.

16:27.731 --> 16:33.778
So, God has created this system by
which you just get completely covered up,

16:34.175 --> 16:36.733
by creating an ego and super-ego

16:36.933 --> 16:42.413
which is just a sort of, you can
say, a by-product of your activities.

16:43.135 --> 16:48.733
Any activity a human-being does, has a reaction.

16:49.111 --> 16:54.993
For example, if he tries to say “no” to
something it has a reaction: he creates his ego.

16:55.193 --> 16:58.584
If he accepts something he creates his super-ego.

16:59.012 --> 17:03.357
This is also done because it is done,

17:03.557 --> 17:08.076
with the help that the brain of the man is made triangular

17:08.276 --> 17:10.495
and prismatic in nature, prismatic.

17:10.696 --> 17:14.620
It’s prism-like plane, and in the prism of the brain

17:14.820 --> 17:20.112
when the rays of God’s divine power flows in,

17:20.386 --> 17:24.067
it goes into refraction, into different angles,

17:24.267 --> 17:28.287
and by the principle of parallelogram of forces,

17:28.487 --> 17:31.370
part of it escapes outside, this side and this side.

17:31.571 --> 17:35.604
That’s why a man can think of the future and of the past,

17:35.804 --> 17:39.323
but the animal does not think of these things.

17:39.524 --> 17:44.140
So that’s how our brain is a specially made one.

17:44.375 --> 17:49.450
It is protected by creating a
ego and a super-ego completely

17:49.650 --> 17:53.793
by which our taalu, where the fontanel bone is covered,

17:53.993 --> 17:56.736
you are separated from the All-pervading Power,

17:56.836 --> 17:59.739
by which you get your independence and freedom,

17:59.941 --> 18:04.567
to act as you like, to use
your brain as you like, to learn,

18:04.894 --> 18:08.143
because the evolution if it has to go any further

18:08.343 --> 18:12.013
this is the transition period when you have to try.

18:14.244 --> 18:18.618
We can say like this for a simile
because simile should not be drawn too far.

18:18.819 --> 18:21.670
But supposing this instrument I prepare.

18:21.871 --> 18:27.342
After preparing it, I first
try it on a small cell separately

18:27.645 --> 18:30.188
and then I put to the mains.

18:30.471 --> 18:33.577
In the same way, first it is tried separately,

18:33.777 --> 18:36.934
individually with an articulation.

18:37.537 --> 18:40.993
The other day I gave a simile of a, of an egg,

18:41.193 --> 18:45.965
which might have sounded little
funny to Marathi people, I don’t know why,

18:46.166 --> 18:48.247
that an egg is created

18:48.447 --> 18:52.347
by articulating it completely, it’s protected.

18:52.656 --> 18:58.842
Till it reaches a complete
stage of its re-birth, is dwijah.

18:59.043 --> 19:03.692
Then only, you see, the mother bird pierces,

19:04.632 --> 19:06.900
the egg and the,

19:07.100 --> 19:11.997
there is a re-birth of the little chick.

19:13.346 --> 19:18.733
In the same way, you are made
protected so that you are made ready.

19:18.958 --> 19:20.567
Ultimately,

19:20.767 --> 19:26.394
you reach a stage where you are just
ready to jump into another state, and it happens.

19:26.850 --> 19:30.455
In the incubator also, if you put these eggs,

19:30.656 --> 19:35.567
with the warmth, you see they
feel the warmth – warmth is the love –

19:35.767 --> 19:40.135
and with that they grow

19:40.438 --> 19:43.219
and at a point all of them hatch out,

19:43.493 --> 19:45.759
I mean not simultaneously,

19:45.959 --> 19:51.140
but we can say little difference, but most of
them hatch out within two three days’ time.

19:51.341 --> 19:54.874
It is in the same manner
today’s Sahaja Yoga is working out,

19:55.212 --> 19:57.506
that you are just ready to have it.

19:57.707 --> 20:01.480
You’ve had a very great past, you’ve been seeking,

20:01.680 --> 20:05.447
you have been going round, you have
no ideas to what you have been doing.

20:05.648 --> 20:09.627
And today you are wearing
ordinary dresses like ordinary people

20:09.827 --> 20:13.469
and today you are here for a lecture with Me

20:13.779 --> 20:16.160
and at this time this happens.

20:17.343 --> 20:21.400
This is the greatest miracle for some people,

20:22.488 --> 20:26.754
but for Me it is just a
happening. It has to happen at this time.

20:26.954 --> 20:31.900
For us if we see lots of flowers
turning into fruits, we never call it a miracle

20:32.259 --> 20:37.026
because we have taken it for granted. So
many miracles of life we have taken it for granted,

20:37.227 --> 20:42.815
but it has to happen to human-beings,
and when it happens it happens like that. -

20:43.204 --> 20:45.620
Naturally for you, you see,

20:45.820 --> 20:49.275
it’s My child’s play. It is for Me, it is My child’s play

20:49.476 --> 20:54.400
because that is My job is to give you
moksha. I am mokshadayani; no doubt about it.

20:54.698 --> 20:59.785
If that is My nature, if that
is My nature then I will do it.

21:00.442 --> 21:03.755
If the nature of the sun is to give you,

21:04.243 --> 21:07.080
the rays of the sun, it will give.

21:07.330 --> 21:10.400
It is not difficult because that is the nature.

21:10.600 --> 21:15.974
You see, if it is your nature as a human
being to see things and colors you will see.

21:16.175 --> 21:18.567
What is so great about it?

21:18.997 --> 21:21.067
What is to be proud about it?

21:21.267 --> 21:25.545
I mean, I don’t understand; if you are that, you are that.

21:26.736 --> 21:30.567
What is there to be higher or
lower? I can’t just understand.

21:30.767 --> 21:35.900
This is all because of a human
ego that a man has evaluations.

21:36.100 --> 21:38.733
He thinks this is higher; that is lower.

21:38.934 --> 21:41.127
In a way human beings are higher than men

21:41.327 --> 21:45.377
and human beings are much higher than gods

21:45.578 --> 21:48.105
and much higher than God Almighty sometimes,

21:48.305 --> 21:51.696
because He has to beg of you to come to Sahaja Yoga,

21:54.291 --> 21:58.170
because unless and until you
are absolutely freely accepting

21:58.371 --> 22:00.336
Sahaja Yoga it doesn’t work out.

22:00.537 --> 22:02.509
You have to be absolutely free.

22:02.709 --> 22:06.466
I cannot entice you. I cannot
hypnotize you. I cannot do anything.

22:06.666 --> 22:08.391
It has to be there.

22:08.663 --> 22:11.233
And that’s why if it works just like that,

22:11.433 --> 22:14.176
why should you feel that there is something wrong in it?

22:14.377 --> 22:17.563
It has worked with so many
people. So many people have felt it.

22:17.763 --> 22:20.600
You will also feel it. It is
your due. So, you are feeling it,

22:20.800 --> 22:23.067
and supposing there is something wrong with the seed

22:23.267 --> 22:27.426
or something wrong with the
flower, then we will correct it also.

22:28.720 --> 22:31.009
May take two days more; doesn’t matter.

22:31.209 --> 22:34.767
It is not something extraordinary for Me.

22:34.968 --> 22:39.067
Yes, it is in a way, because in
all My previous lives I have not done it.

22:39.267 --> 22:41.339
So, I feel very happy.

22:42.045 --> 22:47.233
For example, when you are a leaf
you can’t do the things of a flower,

22:47.590 --> 22:50.930
when you are a root you are not doing that at all,

22:51.130 --> 22:53.733
but when you are a flower

22:53.933 --> 22:56.505
then a bee can come and do it.

22:56.918 --> 23:01.233
What is so much surprising about it?

23:01.433 --> 23:04.659
Because it has been promised. Many a time it has been said.

23:04.859 --> 23:09.567
Even Vivekananda has said that,
“Mother will come and She will do the job.”

23:09.767 --> 23:14.323
He has also said that,
“Buddha is just a part, a little drop.”

23:14.524 --> 23:18.400
He has said all these things. When
you quote Vivekananda, read him properly.

23:18.600 --> 23:21.469
He also says, ‘I can’t do
anything. It’s Mother is going to do.

23:21.669 --> 23:24.125
Everybody is putting on that Mother.”

23:24.351 --> 23:26.939
Shankaracharya said, “Mother will come.”

23:27.264 --> 23:31.723
In the Bible if you read John’s Revelation, written that,

23:31.923 --> 23:35.071
“A Woman will come, and She will be giving,

23:35.272 --> 23:40.067
re-birth and She’ll be afraid of giving
re-birth. She’ll be protecting Her child.”

23:40.267 --> 23:42.236
All these things are there,

23:42.742 --> 23:44.810
and now when the Mother comes in you say,

23:45.010 --> 23:49.107
“Why are you there, Mother?” Now who the
Mother must come with a horn or what should She do?

23:49.606 --> 23:53.320
But if I’m the Mother Who has
to do the job, I have to do the job.

23:54.718 --> 23:58.213
Now you start finding faults with
Me. So, what to do with you people?

23:58.413 --> 24:00.942
I mean, after all, what should I have?

24:01.143 --> 24:03.733
Whatever I thought proper, I have.

24:04.124 --> 24:06.527
What else do you want Me to have?

24:06.728 --> 24:10.400
See if the, if Ganesha has a trunk of a,

24:10.600 --> 24:12.733
elephant it has a meaning,

24:13.235 --> 24:16.248
and if somebody has something else it has a meaning.

24:16.449 --> 24:19.770
We say that Surabhi the cow,

24:19.970 --> 24:22.715
the first cow which appeared in the Brindavana –

24:22.915 --> 24:27.895
in the, in the Vaikuntha stage she
appeared? all the Gods were inside her.

24:28.095 --> 24:33.553
We accept a cow but we can’t accept a
human being who has got these powers.

24:34.672 --> 24:37.652
It’s all right. Don’t accept.
I’m saying not that you should,

24:37.852 --> 24:41.621
flatly accept Me because once I say
that there are many Mataji’s all over now.

24:41.822 --> 24:44.700
What I’m saying, you should feel the vibrations yourself.

24:44.900 --> 24:48.014
You should take them. If you feel them,

24:48.214 --> 24:51.328
if you see the Kundalini rising, that is the first sign.

24:51.528 --> 24:54.896
If you see the Kundalini rising, you should.

24:55.277 --> 25:00.067
When I went to Ambernath there was one Janardhan Maharaj.

25:00.267 --> 25:02.598
He had come, you see, because he had heard about Me.

25:02.798 --> 25:05.353
He came just to take My pareeksha, whatever it is.

25:05.554 --> 25:08.400
So he was sitting near the stage,

25:08.964 --> 25:10.833
and people told Me that,

25:11.033 --> 25:15.167
“He may not accept You, Mataji.” I said,
“Let Me see. If he is a realized soul he may,”

25:15.540 --> 25:19.429
and when I went inside on the
stage he just fell flat on My feet.

25:19.630 --> 25:23.953
Then he told Me, “I saw everybody’s Kundalini
rising as soon as You stepped inside, I could see.”

25:24.153 --> 25:26.220
They can see also.

25:26.460 --> 25:31.805
He saw everybody’s Kundalini rising as soon as I
came in. They would not rise but the Kundalini rose.

25:32.005 --> 25:33.476
“We wish You welcome.”

25:33.676 --> 25:36.528
So, if they know, many people
know. Gagangarh Maharaj knows.

25:36.728 --> 25:39.400
He’s told many people. I have not met him.

25:39.834 --> 25:42.160
He has told many people about Me.

25:43.529 --> 25:45.961
I never met him before. Then I went to see him,

25:46.161 --> 25:49.233
and he talked to Me as if he
would talk to an incarnation, he would.

25:49.433 --> 25:56.067
He never talked to Me as if he would talk to
Mrs. C.P. Srivastava. He didn’t know. He asked Me

25:56.267 --> 26:28.408
[This world has so many bad people. How can you do it? Do they trouble you? How do you incarnate suddenly? We saw Shri chakra opening so we realized that Shri Mataji is born. Akar ,ukar & makar
has also come before Shri chakra. We saw Shri Ganesh, Dattatreya, coming here before you came here. He said it so clearly. It is recorded. He said that Shri Mataji has given you so much –Marathi],

26:28.640 --> 26:30.400
“Why has She given you?

26:30.600 --> 26:32.233
What have you done?

26:32.663 --> 26:35.810
How many of you are going to give your life for Her?

26:36.010 --> 26:39.647
She has given you this precious thing.

26:39.848 --> 26:41.938
You cannot part with one farthing.

26:42.138 --> 26:46.006
What are you going to do for Her?” He scolded all of them.

26:46.403 --> 26:48.900
He said all these things; it is on the tape.

26:49.361 --> 26:53.460
There’s another person Mr. –
his name is Mr. Pralahad Brahamachaari.

26:53.660 --> 26:56.409
He’s from Calicut.

26:56.610 --> 26:59.795
He went to America. He told
people about Me. They know about Me.

26:59.995 --> 27:02.622
He told that, “She has come now. There’s nothing to worry.”

27:02.823 --> 27:06.180
But for you people, you see, you people,

27:06.381 --> 27:11.104
are so egoistical that you cannot
bear to hear such a thing about anyone.

27:11.304 --> 27:14.994
That is the trouble: you are too egoistical.

27:15.863 --> 27:18.859
Adhajal gagri chalkat jaaye.

27:19.060 --> 27:21.733
Empty vessel makes too much sounds.

27:21.933 --> 27:24.148
It’s a sign of emptiness.

27:24.811 --> 27:28.215
You see, they, those people are telling me even that

27:28.415 --> 27:31.567
[aside: what was his name from Ambernath]

27:31.974 --> 27:36.831
Naagnath Baba, he said, “Mataji, they can never accept.

27:37.143 --> 27:42.529
They never accepted any incarnation and they
are not going to accept You, try Your level best.”

27:42.839 --> 27:45.400
And Maharaj says, “For twelve years You try.

27:45.600 --> 27:50.567
If they are all right, then I’ll come down.” Otherwise they
are all hiding themselves. They are afraid of human beings.

27:50.894 --> 27:52.567
Really, it is true.

27:53.148 --> 27:57.946
There are so many like that. Three
very old people came to see Me in Haridwar.

27:58.146 --> 27:59.799
They said the same thing.

28:00.000 --> 28:02.519
Now are you going to behave yourself

28:02.719 --> 28:06.067
or are you going to behave in a manner

28:06.267 --> 28:10.423
that is going to be detrimental
to your progress in spiritual life?

28:10.624 --> 28:14.339
What are you going to do, it is for you to decide.

28:16.958 --> 28:22.180
If you are, if you have read few books
you cannot sit, settle Me into those books.

28:22.381 --> 28:24.598
You see, there is Yoga shastra. Now take Yoga shastra.

28:24.798 --> 28:28.297
Now yesterday he told you
there is saatwik yogashastra this.

28:28.497 --> 28:32.425
What should by yogashastra for Me what is it?

28:32.703 --> 28:36.733
Did Rama read any books or Krishna read
any book and I am going to read any book?

28:36.933 --> 28:40.787
Am I going to use this
Yogashastra? You see, this is for people,

28:40.987 --> 28:43.233
for human beings who have to climb up.

28:43.433 --> 28:47.807
I know everything. So why
should I worry about these things?

28:48.008 --> 28:51.020
I have to just pull you out;
that’s all. I know all the job.

28:51.220 --> 28:54.175
The person who knows the job doesn’t have to do this.

28:55.032 --> 28:57.733
And it comes to this that I have to tell you these things,

28:57.933 --> 29:01.941
you yourselves should realize that if
Mataji is doing like that just by chitta.

29:02.142 --> 29:04.501
Now see today there was, I’ll tell you a case.

29:04.701 --> 29:08.085
Today there yesterday they told me about somebody,

29:08.285 --> 29:12.571
who, who is a brother [Is it our
brother – Marathi] who drinks too much

29:12.772 --> 29:15.315
and he is in Goa. I said, “What to do? How can he come?”

29:15.515 --> 29:19.323
He, he came today [aapo aap]. He came just like that.

29:22.475 --> 29:24.296
Just it is My attention, you see.

29:24.496 --> 29:26.801
If you put anything to My attention it just works.

29:27.001 --> 29:31.233
I don’t have to bother. It is
something like a human being can lift this.

29:31.433 --> 29:34.291
Now an ant will say, “How did you lift it?”

29:34.492 --> 29:37.452
I mean, it is possible for a human being to lift it the,

29:37.652 --> 29:39.999
and for Me it is easy to lift your Kundalini’s

29:40.099 --> 29:42.755
and to do all these miscellaneous things like that

29:42.955 --> 29:45.400
because it is My attention,

29:45.600 --> 29:49.982
My attention, chitta. My attention itself is Ananda.

29:50.182 --> 29:54.163
It is itself, is bliss and it is itself, is the knowledge.

29:54.364 --> 29:57.359
I don’t need any intelligence to know anything because

29:57.559 --> 30:01.534
I know everything in My
head there is all the libraries there.

30:01.734 --> 30:05.390
Now you have read one book that fellow
has found out something from somewhere.

30:05.591 --> 30:09.509
Now how am I to tell you how this mad man
has found out something where from somewhere

30:09.710 --> 30:12.624
and how did he find in darkness he what did he find?

30:12.825 --> 30:15.918
He might have found somebody’s
leg and was thinking it is somebody’s hand.

30:16.119 --> 30:20.342
Now for a person like Me it is
so difficult to go to every person.

30:20.542 --> 30:23.567
Anybody who has read a book
there, a sentence here, will come down.

30:23.767 --> 30:27.814
I said, “Now leave it. Now you want
your realization. Come along have it.”

30:30.370 --> 30:33.421
And then the greatest problem is all this is love.

30:33.621 --> 30:37.733
I mean, I’m just a form of love;
that’s all. It’s nothing but love.

30:38.488 --> 30:42.067
It’s just love, you see, which
expands, gives you vibrations,

30:42.267 --> 30:45.119
again recedes back, expands, it comes back.

30:45.414 --> 30:50.417
It goes in a parabolic like that, what you
call the pradakshina of a shakti you are seeing.

30:50.617 --> 30:53.350
What is shakti is, shakti’s this thing is a parabolic,

30:53.450 --> 30:55.820
and now Einstein is talking about parabolic.

30:56.021 --> 30:59.466
We had a parabolic long time
back here. We knew it was shakti.

31:00.180 --> 31:02.707
See, you can explain all your science and everything.

31:02.907 --> 31:07.073
In this life I learnt English language and
little bit of science and psychology and all that,

31:07.273 --> 31:09.784
but these psychologists are so one-sided people.

31:09.984 --> 31:12.077
Yoga shastras are so one-sided people.

31:12.277 --> 31:14.403
Now they do not match each other.

31:14.603 --> 31:17.400
I’m telling you the basic principle between the two.

31:17.642 --> 31:21.067
Both are human efforts. I’m a different person.

31:21.607 --> 31:24.067
Now what should I do if I’m like that?

31:24.647 --> 31:28.841
How can I become like you?
I mean, if I know how to come up,

31:29.041 --> 31:34.358
how should I become like a little baby and
say, “Oh, no, I must crawl up now gradually.”

31:38.982 --> 31:41.588
I’m an old woman of thousands of years.

31:41.788 --> 31:46.672
So I know everything. You are still
little babies. So how can I become like you?

31:47.866 --> 31:52.369
See, the simple thing and today is
the day I thought I better tell you about it

31:52.569 --> 31:57.772
that you just don’t worry about things
how I do things. I really do it. I cure people.

31:57.973 --> 32:00.567
Now here is a gentleman. He’s a heart patient, ask.

32:01.473 --> 32:04.693
Even before I met him he got quite cured, and I cured him.

32:04.894 --> 32:07.503
There are so many people here who will say that.

32:07.704 --> 32:10.908
[We told about our illness to Mataji – Marathi]

32:11.109 --> 32:15.228
Why? The question, the person who
asked me the question, you ask him.

32:15.656 --> 32:18.692
He has a friend who is in, who’s a Frenchman,

32:18.892 --> 32:22.050
and the Frenchman asked Me a
question about the Western life.

32:22.251 --> 32:26.307
So I didn’t answer it. I started saying
something else. He’s a very intelligent boy, this Rajesh.

32:26.530 --> 32:29.567
So Rajesh said, “Now, you see,
Mataji has not answered your question.

32:29.767 --> 32:32.129
That means She has recorded it and it will act,”

32:32.330 --> 32:34.838
because in his case it has acted.

32:37.901 --> 32:40.507
So God, whatever He has done it is for your good.

32:40.707 --> 32:44.577
He has given you ego and super
-ego not to get spoiled and finished.

32:44.778 --> 32:47.067
Now you can’t blame God for that.

32:47.365 --> 32:52.190
Supposing God has given you light to go that way.

32:52.391 --> 32:55.733
He has told you, “Now take an
independent light to find out that.”

32:55.933 --> 32:59.567
And if you start burning yourself
with that light, what can God do?

33:00.973 --> 33:02.571
It is not God’s mistake.

33:02.925 --> 33:06.266
Many people think that this
ego is horrid. Ego you must have.

33:06.467 --> 33:09.067
Ego you must have. You are not to fight this ego.

33:09.267 --> 33:14.132
Only thing is that your ego should become one
with that of God. That’s all. It’s a very simple thing.

33:17.468 --> 33:19.678
If you just become one with that God –

33:19.878 --> 33:22.698
now supposing this has a ego, how can I talk on this?

33:22.898 --> 33:25.255
I’ll say something; it will say some.

33:25.711 --> 33:29.616
But if it has no ego, its ego
has become one with My saying,

33:29.816 --> 33:34.529
then it carries My voice. It carries
My sayings, everything. It is so simple.

33:34.730 --> 33:37.186
What is so much complicated

33:37.386 --> 33:40.365
when people start telling Me about big, big things,

33:40.565 --> 33:43.905
I really get a fright. I said, what is so complicated?

33:44.160 --> 33:49.295
It is like, you see, somebody wanted
to know how do we make puris, you see.

33:49.626 --> 33:52.465
So a foreigner had come, a lady.

33:52.665 --> 33:55.456
So, she learnt, you know, how you make puris this thing,

33:55.556 --> 33:58.448
and one lady just tried to make fun of the whole thing.

33:58.649 --> 34:01.977
She said, “We make one roti here, one roti there.

34:02.177 --> 34:04.501
Then we put it one on top of another

34:04.701 --> 34:09.509
and then, all sorts of things. And
inside we put, something just to make it big

34:09.709 --> 34:14.444
and then we blow it out with
a phunkni,” and all those things.

34:14.645 --> 34:18.148
So this poor lady, she said that,
“How are you making it just like this,

34:18.348 --> 34:21.074
coming up like that. You are
putting in the kadhai, it’s coming up?”

34:21.275 --> 34:24.683
They said, “It is working out
because it’s the simplest thing to do,”

34:24.884 --> 34:28.351
but for her she said, “No, I was using a blower, blowing in

34:28.552 --> 34:31.370
because I thought that that’s the only way you can do it.”

34:36.815 --> 34:40.680
It is, it is a simple thing for
any housewife to create this thing.

34:40.881 --> 34:45.741
So you see for, when I hear all these
big, big things about yoga, this, that,

34:45.941 --> 34:49.159
then I said, “Baba, what are
you doing?” Now it is very simple.

34:49.359 --> 34:53.349
It is a very simple thing,
but you can’t do it, is the point.

34:53.549 --> 34:56.616
So I’m here. Once you are awakened,

34:56.816 --> 35:00.961
once your light has come, you can do it also. Why not?

35:01.161 --> 35:04.339
And I’ve told Gagangarh
Maharaj, when he started telling Me,

35:04.539 --> 35:08.093
“Why I cannot give realization
to people like this the way these.

35:08.293 --> 35:10.622
I’ve gone so much and I’ve done so much of this thing

35:10.822 --> 35:12.676
[I have given to one & now he is of no use – Marathi]

35:12.877 --> 35:15.733
and useless and how are You,
how are these people doing this?

35:15.933 --> 35:18.785
They will become very egoistical.” I said, “They will not.”

35:19.040 --> 35:23.900
He said, “How do you know?” I said, “They
are made after the pattern of Shri Ganesh;

35:24.786 --> 35:28.694
same powers they will have. Even with the finger moving,

35:28.894 --> 35:31.567
My sons can give realization.

35:31.976 --> 35:36.549
They can. Who are you to
challenge and ask Me?” He kept quiet.

35:36.749 --> 35:39.055
He said, “You are a Mother. Do what you please,

35:39.256 --> 35:43.733
[ but it is not for foolish people” I said - Marathi]

35:44.013 --> 35:46.232
I’m not giving to them.

35:48.073 --> 35:50.400
It is a fantastic thing, that’s why.

35:50.600 --> 35:55.645
You see, it is rather difficult for people to
understand, but anything like this has to be fantastic.

35:55.846 --> 35:58.233
And we have to prove the existence of God.

35:58.433 --> 36:00.900
We have to prove that He exists and He works,

36:01.100 --> 36:04.270
and all those people, chaitanya lahiris and all that,

36:04.470 --> 36:09.476
talks about Kabira and Nanaka
and Hiranya Sanhita and all your yoga,

36:09.676 --> 36:14.132
I’m going to prove it to you before. Have
you ever seen any Kundalini pulsating before?

36:14.332 --> 36:17.625
I will show you the pulsation of a Kundalini.

36:20.379 --> 36:23.445
You have never heard that there are on the fingers

36:23.545 --> 36:26.400
anywhere the vibrations are coming, nothing,

36:26.918 --> 36:30.664
but you have felt it not only
but you can diagnose a person.

36:30.865 --> 36:35.233
You can tell a person what he’s
suffering from. You can cure a person.

36:35.886 --> 36:38.567
Now you will say, “How is it possible?”

36:38.767 --> 36:43.941
and somebody says, “Ten thousand
years before we never heard of these things.”

36:44.142 --> 36:46.626
Everything must happen ten thousand years ago.

36:46.726 --> 36:49.640
Then why are we proceeding further? Better go back.

36:50.211 --> 36:52.310
What kind of a argument is this?

36:52.510 --> 36:56.474
After all, we have discovered going to the moon.

36:56.674 --> 36:59.339
Then we never say, “Why did we go to moon?”

36:59.539 --> 37:02.459
You see, that’s a simple question there. We do not.

37:02.660 --> 37:06.400
But we have to know that
somebody is searching inside for you,

37:07.284 --> 37:09.029
and I’ve found it out.

37:09.230 --> 37:13.900
I’ve visited all these rakshasas also.
I’ve visited all these gurus, all of them,

37:14.100 --> 37:15.900
very nicely befooling them,

37:16.100 --> 37:20.512
and I tried to find out what are they
up too. Now I also know their tricks.

37:20.917 --> 37:23.900
I know what they have done to
you, and that’s how I can correct.

37:24.100 --> 37:27.900
So I’ve studied all the
permutations and combinations and everything,

37:28.100 --> 37:33.960
everything of Kundalini, whatever is possible
because, you know, it’s not so simple with human beings.

37:34.161 --> 37:39.596
They are very, very easily, they are very
easily can be persuaded. They can be enticed.

37:39.796 --> 37:43.900
They can be hypnotized – I cannot be hypnotized –

37:44.323 --> 37:47.950
but you can be very easily
hypnotized. Anybody can hypnotize you like that.

37:48.151 --> 37:51.739
I’ve seen thousands of people
getting hypnotized, taking out their clothes,

37:51.939 --> 37:55.107
dancing, jumping. I’ve
seen some people just making all

37:55.207 --> 37:58.708
kinds of faces, like this, like that, all sorts of things.

37:58.909 --> 38:04.134
It can be done, and the hypnosis is so much that
when they come before Me also they start doing that.

38:04.334 --> 38:07.707
They just get into the
hypnosis because they are used to it.

38:07.908 --> 38:10.774
It’s like Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde.

38:10.974 --> 38:14.900
They just become Mr. Hyde, and
Dr. Jekyll is lost. You become that;

38:15.100 --> 38:16.973
it’s very common.

38:17.178 --> 38:20.370
So for you it is wise to understand that I know

38:20.470 --> 38:23.900
all these things and I will tell you everything.

38:24.100 --> 38:26.437
I’ve got it for you specially

38:26.637 --> 38:29.219
and I know all the permutations and combinations.

38:29.319 --> 38:31.733
You don’t have to do any research about it.

38:32.020 --> 38:34.575
No money is needed to be spent.

38:35.059 --> 38:38.674
Still, you see, there are people who have
been with Me for seven years. Still they are saying,

38:38.874 --> 38:41.762
“Mother, every time You say something we have to learn.”

38:41.963 --> 38:45.822
This is this, this is that, this is
combination, that is combination, everything.

38:46.022 --> 38:52.669
Even five lives will not be sufficient for
you to know a little bit about this knowledge.

38:52.870 --> 38:56.400
So why worry about these
research and things? Just listen to Me

38:56.600 --> 39:02.537
and use your hands and learn and
discover also for yourself that this is the truth,

39:04.234 --> 39:08.136
and don’t listen to everyone,
third person coming round the corner,

39:08.336 --> 39:13.347
somebody selling the paan
there will tell you [Marathi] done.

39:13.855 --> 39:16.733
As if we have no brains at all, you see.

39:17.107 --> 39:21.120
So, you should not listen to
rumors. You are special people.

39:21.320 --> 39:24.669
By God’s grace you have got
vibrations. This is a very big thing.

39:24.870 --> 39:26.992
Those who haven’t got will also get it.

39:27.192 --> 39:29.567
I would request you every day

39:29.767 --> 39:33.485
you have to sit on the water for seven days

39:33.787 --> 39:37.438
to see that you are cleared out now after realization

39:37.638 --> 39:42.295
and also later on whenever you are
tired. It’s better; that’s a bath for you.

39:42.495 --> 39:45.300
Every day do that treatment yourself. It’s a bath.

39:45.500 --> 39:49.419
You cleanse yourself because you gather. I do not gather.

39:49.619 --> 39:52.431
I, nothing happens to Me, but it happens to you.

39:52.631 --> 39:55.817
So, you must have a bath in the night,

39:56.017 --> 39:59.242
take out all the problems on that water, throw it away.

