59:17.933 --> 59:22.411
And I have told you about the Civil
Surgeon of Ahmedabad, what happened to him.

59:22.611 --> 59:26.763
He told Me, “I can’t do all these
nonsensical things.” He was so angry.

59:26.963 --> 59:32.160
“You want me to befool me. I can’t listen to all
this.” I said, “All right, you go ahead. I don’t say,”

59:32.361 --> 59:34.506
and he had become little bit loony.

59:34.706 --> 59:38.079
I said, “All right, I don’t say. All right, don’t bring matka,”

59:38.280 --> 59:43.391
and third day when I was giving a lecture he
was coming there with such a big matka on his head.

59:45.026 --> 59:49.331
So I said, “Doctor,” after the
lecture. I couldn’t help laugh.

59:49.532 --> 59:52.567
After the lecture I said,
“Why did you bring such a big matka?

59:52.767 --> 59:56.477
I had not asked you to bring such a big
matka. I had asked you to bring such a small matka.”

59:56.677 --> 01:00:00.900
He said, “Mataji, your maaya. That’s
how you have killed my ego completely

01:00:01.100 --> 01:00:04.067
because in the market there was no small matka available.

01:00:04.267 --> 01:00:06.900
Only this big one was available.

01:00:10.799 --> 01:00:14.810
So I had to bring such a big matka.”
And he was walking through the whole thing,

01:00:15.010 --> 01:00:17.485
and I was looking at him and I didn’t know where to look.

01:00:17.685 --> 01:00:20.482
I said, “Look at the Civil
Surgeon,” and that convinced people.

01:00:20.682 --> 01:00:25.224
[Oh Civil Surgeon, a big man carrying such a
big matka on his head & going towards Shri Mataji.

01:00:25.425 --> 01:00:28.748
Inside is bhoot or mad? – Marathi]

01:00:28.949 --> 01:00:32.980
Poor Civil Surgeon, but he is a very good man and he’s cured, thank God.

01:00:33.181 --> 01:00:35.733
So it is like this. Then he retired also after that,

01:00:35.933 --> 01:00:39.567
and he is a very good
Sahaja Yogi, still. So it doesn’t matter.

01:00:39.767 --> 01:00:44.148
You know these things are not important.
Mother says, “All right, matka to matkaa.”

01:00:46.173 --> 01:00:51.573
[Shri Krishna cracked Matka. Everything has
a meaning. I will tell you everything & listen it.

01:00:51.773 --> 01:01:02.690
He told Sahaja Yoga in Gokul. It is fun.
Why did he crack matka ? Does it have meaning? -Marathi]

01:01:02.891 --> 01:01:07.728
You will not find it in any book. You
will not know it anymore but Mataji knows.

01:01:07.929 --> 01:01:10.400
She knows all the tricks of Krishna, after all.

01:01:10.600 --> 01:01:12.878
She’s told you all His tricks also.

01:01:13.156 --> 01:01:18.167
[And if it is false you see it.
Now questions are finished – Marathi]

01:01:18.368 --> 01:01:20.765
Seeker: What are the do's and don’ts of Sahaja Yoga?

01:01:20.966 --> 01:01:24.604
Shri Mataji: Don’ts and do's; first and foremost things,

01:01:24.804 --> 01:01:28.067
that a Sahaja yogi cannot smoke or drink.

01:01:29.053 --> 01:01:32.695
One absolutely one hundred percent sure,

01:01:33.458 --> 01:01:36.604
because if you drink or smoke you will find after some time

01:01:36.804 --> 01:01:39.400
you either you’ll lose your
vibrations or you’ll start vomiting.

01:01:39.600 --> 01:01:40.994
You cannot smoke.

01:01:41.195 --> 01:01:44.121
If you smoke your Vishudhdhi will be caught.

01:01:44.322 --> 01:01:47.151
If you drink your Nabhi chakra will be caught

01:01:47.351 --> 01:01:51.525
and whenever you’ll place your hand towards the
photograph all the Nabhi chakra will be burning absolutely.

01:01:51.726 --> 01:01:53.965
So you’ll say, “What is this
happening?” And you’ll give up.

01:01:54.165 --> 01:01:57.049
You sort of, many people
have done it without any difficulty.

01:01:57.249 --> 01:01:59.349
They do not have any difficulty; they just give up.

01:01:59.550 --> 01:02:04.400
So this is one of the most important
things that you have to gradually give up.

01:02:04.600 --> 01:02:10.400
Just take My name; you can work it out. We have
people here, they will tell you they were alcoholics,

01:02:10.600 --> 01:02:13.778
they were taking drugs and
they were doing all kinds of things.

01:02:13.978 --> 01:02:16.859
They’ve given up all that and now
they are absolutely normal people.

01:02:17.060 --> 01:02:21.790
First thing is that: don’t drink and don’t smoke.

01:02:22.033 --> 01:02:24.233
Secondly, don’t fast.

01:02:24.604 --> 01:02:27.067
When Mother is there you are not to fast.

01:02:27.267 --> 01:02:31.563
Only fast on Naraka Chaturdashi; that’s
all. One day you should not have pharal.

01:02:31.763 --> 01:02:36.627
[On that day wake up at 12:00 PM. Eat well – Marathi].

01:02:36.828 --> 01:02:41.080
If you don’t feel like eating, eat
something else but don’t leave your stomach empty.

01:02:41.281 --> 01:02:44.523
You can have some fruit juice or milk or whatever you like.

01:02:44.724 --> 01:02:48.253
These are certain things about the
food and the stomach, Nabhi chakra.

01:02:48.454 --> 01:02:51.124
Secondly, the eyes are very important things

01:02:51.324 --> 01:02:55.505
where you have to be careful not to
move your eyes very fast anywhere.

01:02:55.705 --> 01:02:59.487
Try to keep your eyes steady
and mostly on the Mother Earth.

01:02:59.688 --> 01:03:01.969
You see, you have heard about Lakshamana.

01:03:02.169 --> 01:03:06.839
He never saw the feet of
Sitaji, never, or never saw Her face.

01:03:07.040 --> 01:03:09.869
He only saw Her feet. How can that be?

01:03:10.069 --> 01:03:13.127
He was always living with Her. He had never seen her face;

01:03:13.327 --> 01:03:15.427
he had just seen His feet.

01:03:15.628 --> 01:03:18.433
So, you can imagine what should be the position,

01:03:18.633 --> 01:03:22.633
and for fourteen years he had
to lead a complete brahmacharyaa’s life.

01:03:22.834 --> 01:03:28.310
He just, She was like his mother. He knew
She was Adi Shakti, but he just saw Her feet.

01:03:28.817 --> 01:03:34.094
That should be our case, this thing, that
we should lead a sanctified married life.

01:03:34.295 --> 01:03:36.567
Now supposing somebody is married;

01:03:36.767 --> 01:03:41.733
then he should not run away with other women, and
the other women should not run away with other men.

01:03:41.933 --> 01:03:44.400
And lead a sanctified life,

01:03:44.600 --> 01:03:46.833
create a nest of family,

01:03:47.033 --> 01:03:51.163
a proper family house, try to adopt, compromise,

01:03:51.363 --> 01:03:55.112
adjust, make your wife realize or make your husband realize

01:03:55.313 --> 01:03:57.394
and bring peace in the family

01:03:57.595 --> 01:04:01.284
because there are many great souls
who want to take birth, many of them.

01:04:01.485 --> 01:04:04.567
As soon as you’ll find that such marriages will take place

01:04:04.767 --> 01:04:10.233
they’ve seen now in our case, you can ask
some people from we have here. Ask these girls.

01:04:10.433 --> 01:04:12.817
There I told them that you must marry.

01:04:13.017 --> 01:04:17.108
So, one girl married and she
has a daughter absolutely realized.

01:04:17.308 --> 01:04:19.414
So many people have got realized children.

01:04:19.614 --> 01:04:20.683
[Marathi].

01:04:20.884 --> 01:04:24.567
So many those who got married
like this, they have all realized people.

01:04:24.767 --> 01:04:29.233
So, you must try to get a family life, a proper family,

01:04:29.433 --> 01:04:31.175
proper relationship.

01:04:31.375 --> 01:04:35.866
Do service to your parents, to your
mothers. Don’t find faults with your parents

01:04:36.067 --> 01:04:41.810
and try to be kind to them, also to
the kind to the wife’s mother parents also

01:04:42.011 --> 01:04:47.227
and try to be good in the family. Try
to bring more peace if they are difficult.

01:04:47.427 --> 01:04:52.335
I mean, it’s all right. Don’t spoil the children also.

01:04:52.535 --> 01:04:54.994
Correct them, make them loving.

01:04:55.534 --> 01:04:59.400
Make a nice society. Every
one of you should be the carrier,

01:04:59.600 --> 01:05:01.990
of love of your Mother, everywhere.

01:05:02.191 --> 01:05:05.829
That is one thing, If you are Sahaja yogis

01:05:06.029 --> 01:05:08.576
and if you change and transform in your behavior,

01:05:08.777 --> 01:05:14.094
naturally Sahaja Yoga will have its own
reputation and everybody will start taking to Sahaja Yoga.

01:05:14.295 --> 01:05:17.290
[Doing Sahaj yoga & smuggling doing
is no good. It will not happen – Marathi]

01:05:17.490 --> 01:05:19.287
Impossible.

01:05:20.366 --> 01:05:22.227
If you do anything like that,

01:05:22.427 --> 01:05:24.406
immediately your vibrations will go away.

01:05:24.606 --> 01:05:27.835
There was a gentleman in America, who got realization,

01:05:28.035 --> 01:05:32.236
and he started an ashram
of Sahaja Yoga, started taking money.

01:05:32.436 --> 01:05:36.067
When he came here people told Me,
“Mataji, we get a chakker with this man.

01:05:36.267 --> 01:05:39.754
What’s wrong with him, You tell me.”
Immediately in meditation I knew what was it is.

01:05:39.954 --> 01:05:42.656
I said, “Give Me the pamphlet.” He gave Me the pamphlet.

01:05:42.856 --> 01:05:44.840
I said, “You can’t earn money.

01:05:45.041 --> 01:05:50.322
If you earn money you’ll have a bad time,” and he
had a very bad time after that and he had earlier also.

01:05:50.522 --> 01:05:52.067
Now he’s all right.

01:05:52.267 --> 01:05:56.684
He says, “I will do some other work.”
You cannot earn any money from Sahaja Yoga.

01:05:56.885 --> 01:06:02.067
Do not have Sahaja yogis for business
partnership. No, they are Sahaja yogis.

01:06:02.267 --> 01:06:04.766
Do not use Sahaja Yoga for making money,

01:06:04.967 --> 01:06:08.091
[Someone stole pair of shoes the other day – Marathi].

01:06:08.292 --> 01:06:12.651
You see, this kind of this limit, this
type of people can never be Sahaja yogis.

01:06:12.751 --> 01:06:17.235
You have to be generous people.
You have to be absolutely honest

01:06:18.408 --> 01:06:27.674
[Someone stole my things. It is a
nonsense. Are you to theft? – Marathi].

01:06:27.903 --> 01:06:33.900
They are thieves. They just come here for thieving.
They are not Sahaja yogis. So such people are also there.

01:06:34.100 --> 01:06:39.676
[They take pair of shoes – Marathi]

01:06:39.877 --> 01:06:42.858
This should not be done. There
are Ten Commandments, as you say,

01:06:43.059 --> 01:06:47.757
and you should not take anybody’s
things, and be satisfied in your heart.

01:06:47.958 --> 01:06:52.148
This is a very simple way of doing
things, but you have to lead a chaste life

01:06:52.348 --> 01:06:54.982
and you have to also see chaste things.

01:06:55.182 --> 01:07:00.067
For example, [Bad movies is not good - Marathi]
you will not like it also. Your priorities will change.

01:07:00.267 --> 01:07:03.643
Your friends will change gradually.
You will not like dirty jokes, nothing.

01:07:03.843 --> 01:07:06.067
You’ll just change and you’ll run away from them.

01:07:06.267 --> 01:07:11.400
I’ve seen these foreigners; now they are telling
Me that they just cannot stand all these things now.

01:07:11.600 --> 01:07:15.135
Once upon a time whatever they
could tolerate and enjoy also sometimes,

01:07:15.335 --> 01:07:19.400
they just cannot stand it and bear
it because now you have become saintly.

01:07:19.684 --> 01:07:21.900
You have to be decent people.

01:07:23.382 --> 01:07:37.323
[No need to do politics. Unclear] – Marathi]

01:07:37.823 --> 01:07:41.382
So don’t dabble into all these rumors and frivolous things.

01:07:41.582 --> 01:07:44.900
Don’t waste your precious life. You
are Sahaja yogis. Not a single moment,

01:07:45.100 --> 01:07:47.341
to be wasted on all nonsensical things.

01:07:47.541 --> 01:07:50.259
Every moment should be spent in,

01:07:50.459 --> 01:07:54.608
having dignity for yourself, for others, for loving others.

01:07:54.808 --> 01:07:57.644
[If someone wants something give it to them – Marathi].

01:07:57.844 --> 01:08:02.706
Don’t be misers at all. Miserly
people are against Sahaja Yoga,

01:08:02.907 --> 01:08:05.257
and if miserly people come I give them trouble.

01:08:05.458 --> 01:08:09.567
If you are miserly you get lots of troubles.
So you don’t get miserly, haan, I’m telling you

01:08:09.823 --> 01:08:11.804
and don’t be too talkative also,

01:08:12.005 --> 01:08:15.088
become too talkative and
troublesome. I can stop your talking,

01:08:15.288 --> 01:08:17.474
and if you don’t talk at all that’s also not good.

01:08:17.674 --> 01:08:21.916
Means don’t go to extremes of anything.
These are certain things which you have to know.

01:08:22.117 --> 01:08:26.017
And don’t, women should not dress up like
men, and men should not behave like women.

01:08:26.217 --> 01:08:28.567
All these nonsenses you
should not do. You should be yourself.

01:08:28.767 --> 01:08:34.016
Supposing you are something in something you
are doing you should wear the dresses as you are;

01:08:34.216 --> 01:08:37.560
now no need to wear funny dresses and go round and

01:08:37.760 --> 01:08:40.925
have your hair up to this much or try to show off.

01:08:41.125 --> 01:08:44.466
You see, all these are mythical things. Be normal, natural people

01:08:44.667 --> 01:08:48.760
and lead a normal, natural, decent life, and it’s not so important.

01:08:48.961 --> 01:08:53.067
Food is not so important. Whatever you get you get you eat,

01:08:53.267 --> 01:08:58.351
and don’t talk too much of comfort and
don’t also sleep on the thorns, no, no, no,

01:08:58.552 --> 01:09:00.809
but don’t be absolutely a waster.

01:09:01.009 --> 01:09:04.000
Be in the center; is a very simple thing for Sahaja yogis.

01:09:04.200 --> 01:09:06.901
And you see with your
vibrations if you have to take a decision,

01:09:07.101 --> 01:09:09.639
“Should I take this house or not?” Take the vibrations.

01:09:09.839 --> 01:09:11.567
Anything you see,

01:09:12.659 --> 01:09:16.900
“What should I do? Should I have,
who should I have as a Prime Minister?”

01:09:17.100 --> 01:09:19.944
Now, see for yourself whom do
you want to have a Prime Minister.

01:09:20.144 --> 01:09:24.510
See four people you put in; see the vibrations.
Who has the best? Now, you think of the person.

01:09:24.711 --> 01:09:29.067
He will not be the one the Prime
Minister. You cannot say that he will be

01:09:29.267 --> 01:09:31.865
because maybe that there are so many horrible people.

01:09:32.065 --> 01:09:37.290
In a democracy anybody can be brought in
but the one, who is a good one, is a Sahaja yogi.

01:09:37.490 --> 01:09:39.501
He should be the Prime Minister, and you should ask.

01:09:39.701 --> 01:09:42.490
If the more people ask for it, he may be.

01:09:43.133 --> 01:09:47.408
So, decide everything with vibrations,
for yourself, for collectiveness or anything,

01:09:47.609 --> 01:09:51.045
and the most important is you give it to others.

01:09:51.246 --> 01:09:54.233
And Sahaja Yoga doesn’t work in your houses, families,

01:09:54.433 --> 01:10:01.063
or in small little groups but it works here in Bhartiya
Vidya Bhavan when all of you are here because I’m here.

01:10:01.358 --> 01:10:06.400
It is a collective work. All of you are cells of one body,

01:10:06.853 --> 01:10:11.400
and the more cells are
awakened, the more the body is active.

01:10:11.600 --> 01:10:14.400
So, you have to come together, to be together.

01:10:14.600 --> 01:10:18.508
Love each other. Mix up with
others. Do not form groups, no.

01:10:18.708 --> 01:10:23.900
You should talk to each other very freely,
whatever is your language, nationality or whatever it is.

01:10:24.334 --> 01:10:27.028
And you should mix up with others; is not proper,

01:10:27.228 --> 01:10:30.306
is a sense of insecurity is expressed if you have a group

01:10:30.506 --> 01:10:33.862
[Now we are bramhan so they all
Brahman will sit together -Marathi].

01:10:34.682 --> 01:10:36.914
This kind of a small thing is not there

01:10:37.114 --> 01:10:38.968
[Muslims sitting together in a group – Marathi]

01:10:40.256 --> 01:10:44.626
Foreigners are sitting together in a group like that.

01:10:44.827 --> 01:10:48.863
You see what I’m saying: there should be no grouping done; no need.

01:10:49.434 --> 01:10:52.233
Be open. All of us,

01:10:53.250 --> 01:10:58.581
all of us are born of one Mother, we should
not feel insecure, we should be not together.

01:10:58.782 --> 01:11:01.733
It is not that you should
avoid also, if you are together all right,

01:11:01.933 --> 01:11:04.400
now together is all right we are all brothers and sisters.

01:11:04.600 --> 01:11:08.847
Be very friendly and kind and
do not analyze others and criticize others.

01:11:09.048 --> 01:11:12.765
Better to criticize yourself than to analyze others.

01:11:12.966 --> 01:11:15.947
Will sit down, “He’s like this because like that.”

01:11:16.148 --> 01:11:23.275
[He is like these & like that and what about
you? Pay attention towards yourself. - Marathi]

01:11:23.476 --> 01:11:28.027
We should watch ourselves and not others. Why
somebody is behaving like that, you just don’t worry.

01:11:28.228 --> 01:11:33.553
How are you behaving yourself? Are
you all right? Are your vibrations all right?

01:11:34.433 --> 01:11:37.841
And that’s how with love, patience, understanding,

01:11:38.041 --> 01:11:42.774
I’m sure one day we all will feel the
oneness, all of us, and we should help each other.

01:11:42.974 --> 01:11:45.358
If somebody is sick, we should help. Somebody tells you

01:11:45.558 --> 01:11:47.485
[If he told you that your heart
chakra is catching- Marathi] somebody.

01:11:47.685 --> 01:11:51.067
So, there is nothing to get angry.
Actually, it’s a great thing he has told you

01:11:51.267 --> 01:11:53.900
that he can cure you and you cannot see

01:11:54.679 --> 01:12:06.577
[In the past time this was a problem. If someone is saying that your heart chakra is not clear then he will say, How can you say that my heart chakra is catching ? It is obvious because this finger is burning – Marathi].

01:12:08.618 --> 01:12:11.852
So, it is a story

01:12:12.052 --> 01:12:15.639
told by a person who is not connected.

01:12:15.840 --> 01:12:18.677
So, you should not sort of identify with yourself.

01:12:18.877 --> 01:12:22.510
You should identify yourself with
the eternal life that is within you

01:12:22.710 --> 01:12:24.761
and you are going to enjoy it very much.

01:12:24.961 --> 01:12:29.567
So don’t feel insecure, don’t
have too many desires for something

01:12:29.861 --> 01:12:32.733
and you’ll be surprised that suddenly you’ll find

01:12:32.933 --> 01:12:36.385
[If it happened or not happens nothing matters – Marathi].

01:12:36.861 --> 01:12:41.908
If it works out, well and good; doesn’t work
out well and good, because we are there after all.

01:12:42.109 --> 01:12:45.400
And if the car gets punctured,
all right, we are there after all.

01:12:45.600 --> 01:12:48.958
Even if the car is not there we are there. We are not lost.

01:12:49.307 --> 01:12:54.604
So don’t think of the future, don’t think of
the past but think of the present and enjoy.

01:12:54.804 --> 01:12:57.400
That is the message of Sahaja Yoga,

01:12:58.732 --> 01:13:02.067
and perhaps I’ve covered most of the points for you people,

01:13:02.267 --> 01:13:06.900
and never try to criticize anyone, never, never, never.

01:13:07.100 --> 01:13:11.311
And be firm and know that you have just now crossed,

01:13:11.512 --> 01:13:14.497
so many of you just crossed. So be steady, steadily

01:13:14.697 --> 01:13:17.733
[Look at front –Marathi] what is
going to happen, let us see. Let us see.

01:13:17.933 --> 01:13:20.992
Be with that. Suddenly, don’t be bumptious about it

01:13:21.192 --> 01:13:25.587
and otherwise you’ll be rippled back again,
you see. So gradually grope the whole thing.

01:13:25.787 --> 01:13:28.233
When you have got the mastery over it then grip it.

01:13:28.433 --> 01:13:30.898
But if you are bumptious, anybody can push you down

01:13:31.099 --> 01:13:33.636
saying that [It is not good –Marathi].

01:13:33.837 --> 01:13:35.900
There are many like that. So be careful.

01:13:36.100 --> 01:13:39.948
You see, everybody is trying to push you
down. In this world there are satanic forces,

01:13:40.148 --> 01:13:45.024
and you are very special chosen
people. That’s why you have got vibrations.

01:13:45.224 --> 01:13:48.067
There are so many people in
Bombay but how many have felt it?

01:13:48.267 --> 01:13:50.214
You are the very few who have felt it.

01:13:50.415 --> 01:13:54.457
So be careful about it and
meet together in this same number.

01:13:54.657 --> 01:14:00.900
All of you can be realized fully
if you come together and sit together.

01:14:01.244 --> 01:14:05.319
They say when Mataji is here, they are
here. Then Mataji is only busy all of the time.

01:14:05.519 --> 01:14:10.400
[That’s why I didn’t came to Mumbai this
time. Mataji is curing everyone’s catches – Marathi]

01:14:10.947 --> 01:14:14.400
Those eight or ten people who
have been attending it regularly

01:14:14.600 --> 01:14:17.900
are the best and they are also busy cleaning you

01:14:18.859 --> 01:14:31.692
[Don’t do like that. Put on one day Tuesday.
Today is the last day. I will come back – Marathi].

01:14:32.093 --> 01:14:34.093
Today is the last day

01:14:34.918 --> 01:14:38.067
because I’m going on the 25th evening.

